channel.title: Project Rampage [Release]
channel.description:
[center][b]Project Rampage[/b][/center] [center][b] Hello people. This was the first server i had programmed ages ago. it was lying around in my documents since ages. thought if anyone wanted to use it because I have no use of it anymore. Many people are moving back to 317 old days. This is a very stable 317 PVP Server.[/b][/center]
[b][center] Post Comments Please.[/center][/b]
Features: Note: 317 Server... Perfect PVP with Wilderness LevelsAlmost all Weapon Specials Cooks Assistant Quest - Reward AGS Ability RuneScape Like 2h/GS stances Dark Bow double hit arrow Logout in Combat Delay 100% Potions Perfect Armadyl Godsword Special 100% Player + NPC Poision Splashes Recoiling Vengeance (not real gfx becuz of 317) Multiple Minigames 100% Godwars with Lair of Bosses (Jad, KQ,Dagg King) Barrows MiniGame with accurate chest loot 100% Barrows Breaking Insant Double hit Dragon Dagger Special Old Christmas event - ::christmasevent 100% Assault with Kill Count and Assault Shop Pk Rewards Shop Very Stable PVP Server Emote in Tabs / Teleports in Ancients Book ANTI SYI / googleBOT Limit 1 connection Per IP Connection Filter Enabled Donator Status / Yelling Status
